headline: Quanta Services Named 2025 Top U.S. Solar and Energy Storage Solutions Provider by Solar Power World
summary: Quanta Services, Inc. (NYSE:PWR) announced today that it has been named the top solar solutions provider in the United States by Solar Power World for the second time in three years and the top energy storage solutions provider in Solar Power World's first-ever ranking.
